definitions.explanation_en: A surname of Irish origin, commonly found in English-speaking countries; it does not carry a general semantic meaning outside of its use as a family name.
definitions.explanation_cn: 源自爱尔兰的姓氏，常见于英语国家；作为姓氏使用时无普遍语义含义。
definitions.example_en: Delaney is a well-known actress in Irish cinema.
definitions.example_cn: 德兰尼是爱尔兰电影界知名的女演员。
